### TITLE ###
Multipick errors if empty options
### INPUT ###
opts = []
multipick(opts)
### STDERR ###
error[RAD20000]: Cannot multipick from empty options list
  --> <script>:2:1
  |
1 | opts = []
2 | multipick(opts)
  | ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
  |
   = info: rad docs RAD20000


### EXIT ###
1
### TITLE ###
Multipick errors if min is negative
### INPUT ###
opts = ["Apple", "Banana", "Cherry"]
multipick(opts, min=-1)
### STDERR ###
error[RAD20000]: min must be non-negative, got -1
  --> <script>:2:1
  |
1 | opts = ["Apple", "Banana", "Cherry"]
2 | multipick(opts, min=-1)
  | ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
  |
   = info: rad docs RAD20000


### EXIT ###
1
